sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Client
    participant LSD as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InlineAdapter as GarakInlineEvalAdapter
    participant RemoteAdapter as GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
    participant Garak as garak subprocess
    participant TargetLLM as Target LLM (vLLM)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFP as KFP / DSPA<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FilesAPI as Llama Stack Files API

    Note over User,FilesAPI: Flow 1: Inline Garak Scan (Llama Stack)
    User->>LSD: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>benchmark_id, model
    LSD->>InlineAdapter: run_eval(benchmark_id, model)
    InlineAdapter->>InlineAdapter: deep_merge config + resolve API keys
    InlineAdapter->>Garak: spawn subprocess (os.setsid)<br/>garak --model_type, --probes, --detectors
    Garak->>TargetLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS (configurable)
    TargetLLM-->>Garak: Completion response
    Note over Garak: Run probes + detectors<br/>Generate report
    Garak-->>InlineAdapter: Exit code + scan artifacts
    InlineAdapter->>FilesAPI: Upload reports + results JSON
    InlineAdapter-->>LSD: EvalResult (per-probe scores)
    LSD-->>User: Job ID + results

    Note over User,FilesAPI: Flow 2: Remote KFP Garak Scan (Llama Stack)
    User->>LSD: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>benchmark_id, model (remote provider)
    LSD->>RemoteAdapter: run_eval(benchmark_id, model)
    RemoteAdapter->>RemoteAdapter: Build KFP pipeline definition
    RemoteAdapter->>KFP: Submit pipeline run<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pipeline step pod
    KFPPod->>TargetLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS
    TargetLLM-->>KFPPod: Completion response
    KFPPod->>FilesAPI: Upload scan artifacts<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    RemoteAdapter->>KFP: Poll run status<br/>GET run_id
    KFP-->>RemoteAdapter: Run completed
    RemoteAdapter->>FilesAPI: Retrieve + store results
    RemoteAdapter-->>LSD: EvalResult
    LSD-->>User: Job ID + results

    Note over User,FilesAPI: Flow 3: Intents Benchmark Pipeline (KFP - 6 steps)
    User->>LSD: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>benchmark: intents
    LSD->>RemoteAdapter: run_eval(intents, model)
    RemoteAdapter->>KFP: Submit 6-step pipeline

    Note over KFPPod: Step 1: validate
    KFPPod->>KFPPod: Verify garak + dependencies

    Note over KFPPod,S3: Step 2: resolve_taxonomy
    KFPPod->>S3: Fetch custom taxonomy (if provided)<br/>HTTPS/TLS, AWS IAM

    Note over KFPPod: Step 3: sdg_generate
    KFPPod->>TargetLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions (SDG model)<br/>Auth: SDG_API_KEY
    TargetLLM-->>KFPPod: Synthetic prompts

    Note over KFPPod,S3: Step 4: prepare_prompts
    KFPPod->>S3: Upload raw + normalized CSVs<br/>HTTPS/TLS, AWS IAM

    Note over KFPPod: Step 5: garak_scan (TAP + judge)
    KFPPod->>TargetLLM: Probe target model<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KFPPod->>TargetLLM: TAP attacker model<br/>Auth: ATTACKER_API_KEY
    KFPPod->>TargetLLM: Judge model classification<br/>Auth: JUDGE_API_KEY
    KFPPod->>TargetLLM: Evaluator model<br/>Auth: EVALUATOR_API_KEY

    Note over KFPPod,S3: Step 6: write_kfp_outputs
    KFPPod->>S3: Download + package results<br/>HTTPS/TLS, AWS IAM
    KFPPod-->>KFP: Pipeline complete
    RemoteAdapter->>KFP: Poll → completed
    RemoteAdapter-->>LSD: TBSA scores + per-probe results
    LSD-->>User: Intents evaluation results
